<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七夕.忆江南</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/凤萍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云雀荷池浴水凉，轻摇圆扇罥生香。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">秋风新瘦玉人骨，明月星辉窥金窗。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">淡淡烟浮思喜鹊，幽幽绪乱拢云妆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天边空阔故人远，又见青山送夕阳。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200819/c2a397e153c846099b4c18b4fcf86105.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>天穹下，飘着雨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/凤萍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天穹下飘着珠帘般的小雨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风吹杨柳摇摆着不同的风景</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
