<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《且末》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">浩瀚的大漠中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你是一个不老的神话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">丝路古道璀璨的星空下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你是闪亮的明珠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">车尔臣河是你流淌的血液</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">扎滚鲁克是你生命的见证</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在巍巍昆仑山的注目下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你倔强不屈</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>迷一样的故事</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>亘古离奇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你把古老的岩画刻在阿尔金山上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>千年风沙把来利勒克古城</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>侵蚀成雅丹地貌</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">据说土拉牧场蕴藏着无数珍宝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果你想寻找这方土地的传奇</p>
